name: Arica
Lore: 'Mara Jade posed as a dancer at Jabba''s Palace in an attempt to complete her master''s task and kill Luke. Musician. Spy. Unable to convince Jabba to take her on his skiff.',
Text: 'Deploys only to a site as an Undercover spy. While present, reduces Luke''s forfeit and immunity to attrition by 2 here. During opponent''s control phase, Arica may ''break cover'' to fire one weapon (for free). Immune to attrition < 4.',
